'''Rellidir''' was the capital of [[Tralus/Legends|Tralus]]<ref name="TCSWE">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref>. It contained the [[Navos Center for the Performing Arts]] and the [[Terkury Housing Complex]]. In [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]], it had a population of 1 million, the largest center on the world.

==Behind the scenes==
Although ''Betrayal'' names it Rellidir, all earlier sources called it '''Rendilir'''.

